{"tid":1142502,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"考牌 1 take pass 心得分享","createTime":"2019-05-07T06:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T09:24:19.000Z","uid":123335,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f64194a19c595ee5140407f474543ce1d93feb6f","tid":1142502,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:11:35.000Z","msg":"就係考車之前，去做蹲舉重訓 （Squat）<br />\n<br />\n低、中強度都會有效<br />\n其中以高強度為最佳 <br />\n<br />\n以下係學術研究部分：<br />\n根據譚弼中既研究（2015），<span style=\"color: red;\">高強度蹲舉訓練（Squat）對睪固酮濃度顯著地有立即及持續增加。</span><br />\n而低強度及中強度訓練對總睪固酮濃度亦有立即性增加。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">P.s. <span style=\"color: red;\">高強度 = 5 RM訓練組</span><br />\n中強度 = 10 RM訓練組<br />\n低強度 = 15 RM訓練組</span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n咁究竟提升睪固酮對考車有咩幫助？<br />\n<br />\n1）你會有更 sharp 既頭腦去應付所有臨場突發情況，無懼世事變改。 [e.g. 阿婆衝出嚟執橙、的士司機係後面推你架車、小巴司機cut線唔打燈 ... etc ] <br />\n<br />\n2）你會更有自信地應付考牌官喺隔離揸住支筆tick tick tick 既壓力 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iaG6sRA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiaG6sRA.jpg&h=84998d52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<ins># 結論：</ins><br />\n考車前做蹲舉重訓 （Squat）去操腳，對你考車時既臨場發揮有莫大嘅加成，大大提升 1 take pass 既機會 <br />\n<br />\n健身，健心。<br />\n考牌 1 take pass <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Source: <br />\nTan, Pi-Chung (2015), The Effect of Squat Resistance Training for Healthy Men in Arteriosclerosis Degree and Total Testosterone Concentration, <a href=\"http://ir.lib.pccu.edu.tw/handle/987654321/30274?layout.style=mobile\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fir.lib.pccu.edu.tw%2Fhandle%2F987654321%2F30274%3Flayout.style%3Dmobile&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HI429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=76ad333e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ir.lib.pccu.edu.tw/handle/987654321/30274?layout.style=mobile</a> </span>"},{"pid":"9367cd85b85f92acb06df22e834cffec763a4e6b","tid":1142502,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:12:08.000Z","msg":"收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f00cce9185e3c284055b00536d8838eef526201","tid":1142502,"uid":120481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:13:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e899441738d9481535cc1a679be4144001750867","tid":1142502,"uid":120481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:13:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53089614f355e20b50421e166f0cc8e6b73af98a","tid":1142502,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e899441738d9481535cc1a679be4144001750867","tid":1142502,"uid":120481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:13:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:14:39.000Z","msg":"一陣放工操 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84366e4b292e5f2e5e3cd64805ee1d35ab0c9947","tid":1142502,"uid":250143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:14:39.000Z","msg":"但我個師傅話我 有玩健身 影響左揸車d踩極力既力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e6cd1addef56cc2dc5ac338a24a8d2618022f5","tid":1142502,"uid":120481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:16:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2495cfb661480c9e99df473f804740953119dc45","tid":1142502,"uid":79023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:18:48.000Z","msg":"呢個真，慢車果陣吊極力子都無咁易腳震丫"},{"pid":"7de8ad60e8705a3a9f0b02fd5e23a3d2a22582a8","tid":1142502,"uid":221955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim